node.text:
To celebrate international yoga day, we invited our IIN ambassador @withyohanna to hold an online yoga class for you. 🧘‍♀️ 

Yohanna is a yoga teacher and wellness coach based in Stockholm, Sweden. After healing from burnout and eating disorder, she now guides ambitious women to balanced and meaningful lives through coaching, events and retreats. 🙏🏻

Yohanna happily shares her experience of being a student of IIN and welcome you to reach out via IG to ask questions. Remember to mention “Yohanna Mannelqvist” when you book your program to receive her ambassador discount of $2000! 💕🙌🏼

node.text:
We got kicked out at the end of our yin yoga stretch, but had a great conversation about the importance of breathwork & stretching to overall mental & physical wellness. 

We also discussed my experience with IIN, what led me to the program & how it’s shaped my life, health & career. 

You can follow me @coachcalie to continue the discussion. And don’t miss out on the opportunity yet the IIN sample class linked in my Instagram profile.

node.text:
Build strength + flexibility with IIN Health Coach, @theholistictrinity 

for strength 
1. narrow arm push-ups 
2. wide arm push-ups 
3. forearm plank to pike 
4. high plank rocks
5. tricep dips
6. forearm stand one leg kick-ups

do sets of 10-15 and repeat as many times as feels right 

for flexibility 
1. thread the needle 
2. cross body stretch 
3. forearm wheel

#primaryfood #nutritionschool

node.text:
It's National Chocolate Chip Cookie Day!There's no reason you can't enjoy your favorite treats, like this recipe for Three Ingredient Cookies. Yum! 🍪@fivesechealth 

Recipe (from the Fivesec Health app)
- 1 cup dates (soak in hot water if using medjool)
- 1 cup almond flour
Mash it up, combine, roll into balls and press out on an oven tray lined with parchment paper. Add vegan chocolate chips and bake for 14-15 minute on 175C/347F 
#nutritionschool #healthyfood

node.text:
“I did it 🎉👩🏼‍🎓

I followed my passion and invested in myself. Becoming an Integrative Nutrition Health Coach with the world's largest @nutritionschool <https://www.instagram.com/nutritionschool/> has been an incredible journey of learning, personal development, reflection and growth.

Now I'm privileged to be part of a ripple effect in the health industry. Guiding people to their version of healthy by focusing not just on what we eat, but all aspects of our life. Healthy relationships, physical activity, a fulfilling career and spiritual practice are all part of living a balanced and healthy lifestyle.

I'm also halfway through a yoga teacher training course so watch this space 🤗 I can't wait to share it with you all 🙏” - IIN Health Coach @thehappyrepublic

Who else has a garden full of fresh zucchini? Try this delicious zoodle recipe by @sproutingvitality to liven up your Monday. 

Ingredients:
-1 lb Ground Pork, I love to use McIntyre Pastures. A local farm here in Idaho where you can taste the quality of their farming in every bite.
-Drizzle Avocado oil from Chosen Foods 
-2 Fresh zucchini from my garden, zoodled
-Fresh basil from my garden 

Remaining ingredients are from Trader Joe's 
-2 containers Bruschetta
-2 Tbsp Herbs de Province 
-Onion diced 
-Jar fire roasted bell peppers, diced 
-Container burrata cheese
-1 container mushrooms, I like shiitake, sliced 
-1 Tbsp minced garlic 
-Jar chili onion crunch sauce 
-bottle balsamic glaze

Find the full recipe at: 
https://sprouting-vitality.com/the-best-zoodles-to-have-on-your-plate/

#nutritionschool #healthyrecipes
